00:08:38.085 --> 00:08:41.022 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I know that you'll develop</i>
 <i>your skills.</i>

00:08:41.055 --> 00:08:42.556 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I know that without me,</i>

00:08:42.590 --> 00:08:45.026 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>you'll become the greatest</i>
 <i>player ever.</i>

00:08:46.727 --> 00:08:49.530 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Today is probably</i>
 <i>the last day...</i>

00:08:49.563 --> 00:08:52.266 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>that you and I</i>
 <i>see each other.</i>

00:08:54.035 --> 00:08:54.869 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa...</i>

00:08:55.436 --> 00:08:56.637 position:35% line:89% align:start
