 <i>with Roberto...</i>

00:09:09.617 --> 00:09:11.952 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>was my only motivation</i>
 <i>this whole time.</i>

00:09:13.187 --> 00:09:13.888 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:09:13.921 --> 00:09:14.955 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:14.989 --> 00:09:18.926 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>And I won the tournament</i>
 <i>just like I promised.</i>

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:20.161 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:09:20.194 --> 00:09:22.129 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why did you abandon me?!</i>

00:09:27.502 --> 00:09:34.975 position:41% line:89% align:start
[pants]

00:09:35.009 --> 00:09:35.776 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:35.810 --> 00:09:37.011 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Roberto!</i>

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.881 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
[panting]

00:09:40.915 --> 00:09:41.916 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Roberto!</i>

00:09:44.151 --> 00:09:45.953 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Roberto!</i>

00:09:45.986 --> 00:09:49.056 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:09:49.690 --> 00:09:51.358 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Roberto!</i>

00:09:51.392 --> 00:09:54.662 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:09:55.696 --> 00:09:56.931 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Roberto...</i>

00:09:57.998 --> 00:09:58.999 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>Why?</i>

00:10:00.101 --> 00:10:00.868 position:44% line:89% align:start
[sob]

00:10:00.901 --> 00:10:04.171 position:21% line:83% align:start
Roberto, why did you
abandon me?!

00:10:04.205 --> 00:10:06.740 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:10:07.908 --> 00:10:11.011 position:13% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>We'll be right back</i>
 <i>with Captain Tsubasa.</i>

00:10:14.815 --> 00:10:16.317 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>And we're back!</i>

00:10:18.018 --> 00:10:20.221 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Sometime after</i>
 <i>the national tournament.</i>

00:10:28.863 --> 00:10:29.864 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:31.566 --> 00:10:32.833 position:24% line:89% align:start
Son, did you finish

00:10:32.867 --> 00:10:34.702 position:21% line:83% align:start
-packing your things?
-Oh...

00:10:34.735 --> 00:10:37.371 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, I'm almost
done here.

00:10:37.404 --> 00:10:39.039 position:13% line:89% align:start
We have to leave soon, Son.

00:10:39.073 --> 00:10:39.974 position:33% line:89% align:start
I know, Dad.

00:10:40.774 --> 00:10:43.043 position:30% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>Nankatsu</i>
 <i>Soccer Club.</i>

00:10:44.812 --> 00:10:45.045 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey, everybody,

00:10:46.280 --> 00:10:48.649 position:13% line:83% align:start
sorry to have made you come
all the way to our school.

00:10:48.682 --> 00:10:49.884 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't sweat it, Ryo.

00:10:49.917 --> 00:10:52.587 position:19% line:83% align:start
Misaki is an important
team member to all of us.

00:10:52.621 --> 00:10:54.655 position:16% line:83% align:start
We wouldn't let him leave
just like that.

00:10:54.688 --> 00:10:56.257 position:21% line:83% align:start
I even managed to get
Wakabayashi

00:10:56.290 --> 00:10:57.758 position:24% line:89% align:start
to sign it as well.

00:10:57.791 --> 00:10:58.859 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Takeshi]
He'll come tomorrow

00:10:58.893 --> 00:10:59.960 position:19% line:89% align:start
to say bye to him too.

00:11:00.761 --> 00:11:01.829 position:21% line:89% align:start
It looks like Tsubasa

00:11:01.862 --> 00:11:03.497 position:27% line:83% align:start
won't be able to
make it today.

00:11:03.532 --> 00:11:04.665 position:33% line:89% align:start
Maybe not...

00:11:04.698 --> 00:11:07.768 position:13% line:83% align:start
He's still pretty depressed
about Roberto.

00:11:07.801 --> 00:11:09.737 position:19% line:89% align:start
I hope he's doing okay.

00:11:09.770 --> 00:11:11.472 position:19% line:89% align:start
I would like to know...

00:11:11.506 --> 00:11:13.841 position:19% line:83% align:start
what he'll do now that
Roberto's gone.

00:11:13.874 --> 00:11:14.942 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hmm...
-Hmm...

00:11:15.577 --> 00:11:16.777 position:16% line:89% align:start
I heard somewhere that...

00:11:16.810 --> 00:11:20.649 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa was recruited
to play for Toho Academy.

00:11:20.681 --> 00:11:21.849 position:30% line:89% align:start
I heard it too.

00:11:21.882 --> 00:11:22.950 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's incredible.

00:11:22.983 --> 00:11:24.752 position:16% line:83% align:start
Not everyone has the luck
to be invited

00:11:24.785 --> 00:11:26.320 position:19% line:89% align:start
to play for their team.

00:11:26.353 --> 00:11:27.522 position:13% line:89% align:start
Just because he got invited

00:11:27.556 --> 00:11:28.722 position:33% line:83% align:start
doesn't mean
he'll accept it.

00:11:28.756 --> 00:11:30.024 position:21% line:89% align:start
If he stays with us,

00:11:30.057 --> 00:11:32.927 position:21% line:83% align:start
we can be in Nankatsu
Middle school's youth team.

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:34.195 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, but with his talent
and skill,

00:11:34.228 --> 00:11:35.996 position:13% line:83% align:start
it would be a shame for him
to have to stay

00:11:36.030 --> 00:11:38.232 position:24% line:83% align:start
in a public school
like ours, you know.

00:11:38.265 --> 00:11:40.734 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, at least now
we'll know just...

00:11:40.768 --> 00:11:42.069 position:24% line:83% align:start
which of the teams
is better.

00:11:42.102 --> 00:11:45.940 position:16% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu's original team
or Shutetsu right?

00:11:45.973 --> 00:11:46.874 position:41% line:89% align:start
Aww...

00:11:46.907 --> 00:11:49.310 position:13% line:83% align:start
Huh? Are you okay, Shingo?
What's wrong?

00:11:49.343 --> 00:11:50.411 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's just...

00:11:50.444 --> 00:11:51.946 position:33% line:83% align:start
if we go back
to our school...

00:11:51.979 --> 00:11:55.082 position:27% line:83% align:start
the Nankatsu team
will be completely...

00:11:55.115 --> 00:11:55.950 position:33% line:89% align:start
divided now.

00:11:56.651 --> 00:11:58.620 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hmm...
-Hmm...

00:11:58.653 --> 00:12:00.487 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yeah, and that's
exactly why...

00:12:00.522 --> 00:12:01.755 position:27% line:89% align:start
we need Misaki...

00:12:01.789 --> 00:12:04.892 position:16% line:83% align:start
to receive a message from
Tsubasa with this ball.

00:12:09.330 --> 00:12:09.496 position:30% line:89% align:start
So then Taro...

00:12:10.798 --> 00:12:13.267 position:16% line:83% align:start
did you tell them we'd be
leaving tomorrow morning?

00:12:13.300 --> 00:12:14.301 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:12:15.670 --> 00:12:16.737 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-Huh?

00:12:16.770 --> 00:12:18.573 position:35% line:83% align:start
Look there,
it's Misaki!

00:12:18.607 --> 00:12:19.541 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:12:19.574 --> 00:12:20.441 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:20.474 --> 00:12:21.543 position:35% line:89% align:start
Everyone...

00:12:21.576 --> 00:12:22.644 position:41% line:89% align:start
Misaki!

00:12:22.677 --> 00:12:23.811 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why're you carrying
your luggage?

00:12:23.844 --> 00:12:25.212 position:21% line:83% align:start
You were supposed to
leave tomorrow.

00:12:25.246 --> 00:12:26.247 position:21% line:89% align:start
Why'd you lie to us?

00:12:26.747 --> 00:12:28.048 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:12:28.082 --> 00:12:30.117 position:13% line:83% align:start
I thought it'd be too hard
to say goodbye to you guys

00:12:30.150 --> 00:12:31.785 position:27% line:83% align:start
after everything
we've been through.

00:12:31.819 --> 00:12:34.054 position:24% line:83% align:start
That would've been
messed up, Misaki!

00:12:34.088 --> 00:12:34.522 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry.

00:12:35.657 --> 00:12:37.726 position:24% line:83% align:start
Ryo, we can't keep
waiting any longer.

00:12:37.758 --> 00:12:38.959 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I know we can't.

00:12:38.993 --> 00:12:41.262 position:27% line:83% align:start
Misaki, what time
is your bus leaving?

00:12:41.295 --> 00:12:42.029 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:12:42.062 --> 00:12:44.131 position:24% line:83% align:start
Like in 15 minutes
I suppose.

00:12:44.164 --> 00:12:45.899 position:35% line:83% align:start
Okay then,
I'm going to have to

00:12:45.933 --> 00:12:48.503 position:35% line:83% align:start
run over to
Tsubasa's house real fast.

00:12:48.536 --> 00:12:50.471 position:30% line:83% align:start
And meanwhile,
we'll go get Genzo.

00:12:50.505 --> 00:12:51.472 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

00:12:53.340 --> 00:12:54.441 position:27% line:89% align:start
All my friends...

00:12:55.809 --> 00:12:57.545 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Ryo] What?
He's not here?!

00:12:57.579 --> 00:12:58.879 position:24% line:83% align:start
Yeah, he got out of
the house early.

00:12:58.912 --> 00:13:00.881 position:21% line:83% align:start
I think he was headed
towards the river.

00:13:00.914 --> 00:13:01.882 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is something wrong?

00:13:01.915 --> 00:13:02.916 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's an emergency.

00:13:02.950 --> 00:13:04.519 position:21% line:89% align:start
Misaki leaves today!

00:13:04.552 --> 00:13:05.553 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?!

00:13:11.292 --> 00:13:14.061 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Roberto left behind</i>
 <i>this book with the letter.</i>

00:13:14.094 --> 00:13:16.030 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>These are all the notes</i>
 <i>he took.</i>

00:13:16.897 --> 00:13:18.232 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Advice and ways to practice.</i>

00:13:19.534 --> 00:13:21.869 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's had this book with him</i>
 <i>since he started his career</i>

00:13:21.902 --> 00:13:23.871 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>as a professional</i>
 <i>soccer player,</i>

00:13:23.904 --> 00:13:26.006 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and now, I've inherit it.</i>

00:13:26.807 --> 00:13:28.008 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>But...</i>

00:13:31.145 --> 00:13:32.146 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Roberto...</i>

00:13:32.681 --> 00:13:33.847 position:44% line:89% align:start
 <i>I...</i>

00:13:33.881 --> 00:13:36.751 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I just wanted to go</i>
 <i>to Brazil with you.</i>

00:13:36.785 --> 00:13:38.419 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[Ryo] Tsubasa!
-Huh?

00:13:38.452 --> 00:13:40.755 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:13:40.789 --> 00:13:42.289 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ishizaki...

00:13:42.323 --> 00:13:43.824 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's an emergency!

00:13:43.857 --> 00:13:45.159 position:24% line:89% align:start
Misaki is leaving.

00:13:45.192 --> 00:13:46.193 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:13:48.797 --> 00:13:49.597 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:13:50.565 --> 00:13:51.999 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Manabu]
The bus is on its way.

00:13:58.339 --> 00:13:59.039 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:02.443 position:21% line:83% align:start
Ishizaki, you need to
hurry up.

00:14:02.476 --> 00:14:03.310 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:14:04.111 --> 00:14:06.480 position:30% line:83% align:start
Get on the bus.
It's time to go.

00:14:06.514 --> 00:14:07.582 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:14:08.849 --> 00:14:10.785 position:13% line:83% align:start
Everyone, please take care
of yourselves.

00:14:10.819 --> 00:14:12.419 position:16% line:83% align:start
So you're really leaving,
Taro?

00:14:12.453 --> 00:14:13.320 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:14:13.354 --> 00:14:15.557 position:24% line:83% align:start
Please let Tsubasa
know I said goodbye.

00:14:17.157 --> 00:14:18.526 position:41% line:89% align:start
[pants]

00:14:19.561 --> 00:14:21.095 position:16% line:89% align:start
Have a safe trip, Misaki.

00:14:21.128 --> 00:14:22.597 position:19% line:89% align:start
You take care, Misaki.

00:14:22.630 --> 00:14:23.964 position:21% line:89% align:start
Take care, all right?

00:14:26.568 --> 00:14:27.836 position:35% line:89% align:start
Take care!

00:14:27.868 --> 00:14:30.337 position:13% line:83% align:start
-Be good out there, Misaki!
-Ah!

00:14:32.473 --> 00:14:33.775 position:24% line:83% align:start
-[Tsubasa] Misaki!
-Huh?

00:14:33.808 --> 00:14:37.545 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:14:39.647 --> 00:14:40.648 position:47% line:89% align:start
Oh!

00:14:40.682 --> 00:14:41.882 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[Taro] Tsubasa!
-[panting]

00:14:41.915 --> 00:14:42.916 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:14:42.950 --> 00:14:44.753 position:41% line:83% align:start
Misaki!
[pants]

00:14:44.786 --> 00:14:45.986 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ah...

00:14:46.487 --> 00:14:48.155 position:41% line:89% align:start
Misaki!

00:14:48.857 --> 00:14:49.557 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:14:50.290 --> 00:14:52.092 position:38% line:83% align:start
Goodbye!
Take care, Tsubasa!

00:14:52.126 --> 00:14:53.894 position:16% line:89% align:start
Everything will work out!

00:14:53.927 --> 00:14:55.295 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[panting]
-Tsubasa!

00:14:55.329 --> 00:14:56.363 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here!

00:14:56.964 --> 00:14:59.299 position:21% line:89% align:start
Taro, catch the ball!

00:14:59.333 --> 00:15:00.401 position:44% line:89% align:start
Here!

00:15:00.434 --> 00:15:02.136 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:03.505 --> 00:15:04.506 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:15:06.106 --> 00:15:06.841 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:15:06.875 --> 00:15:08.643 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>To the best partner.</i>

00:15:08.676 --> 00:15:09.943 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa.</i>

00:15:09.977 --> 00:15:11.613 position:30% line:89% align:start
Goodbye, Taro.

00:15:12.446 --> 00:15:13.914 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh... Ah!

00:15:14.849 --> 00:15:17.652 position:27% line:83% align:start
Thank you so much
for everything, Tsubasa.

00:15:17.685 --> 00:15:20.053 position:13% line:89% align:start
Thanks so much, everybody!

00:15:26.427 --> 00:15:27.896 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Take care, Taro.</i>

00:15:27.928 --> 00:15:29.363 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>We'll see each other soon.</i>

00:15:30.931 --> 00:15:31.833 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
Taro isn't the only one

00:15:31.866 --> 00:15:33.033 position:27% line:83% align:start
-that's leaving.
-Huh?

00:15:33.967 --> 00:15:35.503 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
Genzo...

00:15:35.537 --> 00:15:36.604 position:16% line:89% align:start
What do you mean by that?

00:15:37.739 --> 00:15:39.072 position:13% line:89% align:start
What're you talking about?

00:15:39.106 --> 00:15:40.842 position:19% line:89% align:start
Well, it's just that...

00:15:40.875 --> 00:15:42.443 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm going to play
in Germany.

00:15:45.513 --> 00:15:46.480 position:38% line:89% align:start
Genzo...

00:15:46.514 --> 00:15:49.383 position:27% line:83% align:start
Next school year,
you'll be in middle school.

00:15:49.416 --> 00:15:50.150 position:38% line:89% align:start
I know...

00:15:51.084 --> 00:15:53.655 position:24% line:83% align:start
I have to tell you
something important.

00:15:53.688 --> 00:15:56.558 position:13% line:83% align:start
Unfortunately, I can't keep
being your trainer here.

00:15:56.591 --> 00:15:58.392 position:24% line:83% align:start
-I'm deeply sorry.
-What?!

00:15:58.425 --> 00:16:00.562 position:24% line:83% align:start
The Japanese soccer
association

00:16:00.595 --> 00:16:03.631 position:19% line:83% align:start
has requested for me to
attend a special seminar

00:16:03.665 --> 00:16:05.733 position:35% line:83% align:start
of trainers
hosted in Germany.

00:16:05.767 --> 00:16:06.901 position:35% line:83% align:start
The reason
they're doing this

00:16:06.935 --> 00:16:09.303 position:24% line:83% align:start
is so we can better
the level of the players

00:16:09.336 --> 00:16:10.270 position:30% line:89% align:start
here in Japan.

00:16:10.304 --> 00:16:13.073 position:41% line:83% align:start
And...
when are you leaving?

00:16:13.106 --> 00:16:15.375 position:30% line:83% align:start
I have to leave
in the beginning of spring.

00:16:15.409 --> 00:16:17.411 position:21% line:83% align:start
And I'll be spending
two whole years there

00:16:17.444 --> 00:16:19.213 position:24% line:83% align:start
learning everything
about the style of play

00:16:19.246 --> 00:16:21.048 position:27% line:83% align:start
they're teaching
in Europe nowadays.

00:16:21.916 --> 00:16:23.718 position:30% line:83% align:start
But I wanted to
ask you this...

00:16:23.751 --> 00:16:24.819 position:30% line:89% align:start
Genzo, tell me,

00:16:24.853 --> 00:16:27.454 position:27% line:83% align:start
would you like to
come to Germany with me?

00:16:27.488 --> 00:16:28.489 position:27% line:89% align:start
Are you serious?

00:16:29.624 --> 00:16:30.792 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-No...

00:16:30.825 --> 00:16:33.260 position:19% line:83% align:start
So then you're leaving
to Germany now?

00:16:33.293 --> 00:16:36.063 position:13% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa, when I heard that
you were going to Brazil,

00:16:36.096 --> 00:16:37.732 position:24% line:83% align:start
I started to think
a lot about

00:16:37.765 --> 00:16:38.633 position:19% line:89% align:start
my professional career.

00:16:39.567 --> 00:16:41.703 position:30% line:83% align:start
If I want to be
a professional player,

00:16:41.736 --> 00:16:45.072 position:7% line:83% align:start
I have to learn to play soccer
at the world level.

00:16:45.105 --> 00:16:46.774 position:27% line:83% align:start
The soccer league
in Germany

00:16:46.808 --> 00:16:48.910 position:24% line:83% align:start
is one of the best
in the world.

00:16:48.943 --> 00:16:52.112 position:19% line:83% align:start
And they have the best
goalies to ever live.

00:16:52.145 --> 00:16:54.214 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's the main reason
I want to go.

00:16:55.249 --> 00:16:58.318 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wish to be the best
goalkeeper in the world.

00:16:58.352 --> 00:16:59.419 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Wakabayashi...
-But Captain,

00:16:59.453 --> 00:17:00.454 position:27% line:89% align:start
it's just that--

00:17:03.056 --> 00:17:04.759 position:21% line:89% align:start
Genzo, I wish you...

00:17:04.792 --> 00:17:06.126 position:27% line:89% align:start
the best of luck.

00:17:06.159 --> 00:17:08.997 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm sure nothing will get
on the way of your dreams.

00:17:09.029 --> 00:17:10.798 position:35% line:83% align:start
Thank you.
I'll do my best.

00:17:10.832 --> 00:17:11.666 position:21% line:89% align:start
But before I leave...

00:17:12.499 --> 00:17:15.035 position:19% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa, I'm asking you
to please

00:17:15.068 --> 00:17:17.204 position:16% line:83% align:start
let me have one last duel
against you.

00:17:17.237 --> 00:17:18.038 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:17:18.071 --> 00:17:20.842 position:30% line:83% align:start
I was about to
ask the same of you.

00:17:20.875 --> 00:17:22.476 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>One week later.</i>

00:17:30.450 --> 00:17:32.921 position:24% line:83% align:start
The first time that
you and I saw each other,

00:17:32.954 --> 00:17:35.857 position:21% line:83% align:start
it was in this exact
same field, my friend.

00:17:35.890 --> 00:17:37.692 position:19% line:89% align:start
And here we are again.

00:17:37.725 --> 00:17:38.660 position:33% line:89% align:start
The goodbye.

00:17:39.226 --> 00:17:40.628 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm ready, Tsubasa.

00:17:40.662 --> 00:17:42.095 position:13% line:89% align:start
Shoot whenever you'd like.

00:17:42.129 --> 00:17:43.497 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm coming.

00:17:43.531 --> 00:17:44.832 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa.

00:17:44.866 --> 00:17:46.199 position:33% line:89% align:start
And Genzo...

00:17:46.801 --> 00:17:48.302 position:35% line:89% align:start
Here I go!

00:17:52.707 --> 00:17:53.307 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:17:53.340 --> 00:17:55.475 position:16% line:89% align:start
Genzo, prepare yourself.

00:17:56.109 --> 00:17:57.177 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>No one will score on me</i>

00:17:57.210 --> 00:17:59.146 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>from outside</i>
 <i>the goalkeeper's box.</i>

00:18:00.915 --> 00:18:02.115 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:18:02.784 --> 00:18:03.518 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:18:04.184 --> 00:18:06.754 position:13% line:89% align:start
It... It slipped past him!

00:18:06.788 --> 00:18:07.589 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-It can't be...

00:18:07.622 --> 00:18:08.823 position:21% line:89% align:start
It hit the goal post.

00:18:10.058 --> 00:18:11.258 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:18:15.997 --> 00:18:18.298 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:18:18.332 --> 00:18:20.233 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:18:20.267 --> 00:18:22.637 position:21% line:83% align:start
-He... He stopped it.
-[groan]

00:18:24.973 --> 00:18:26.874 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:18:27.575 --> 00:18:28.910 position:27% line:89% align:start
Did you see that?

00:18:28.943 --> 00:18:30.344 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:18:30.377 --> 00:18:32.814 position:19% line:83% align:start
[groan] I didn't expect
any less from you.

00:18:32.847 --> 00:18:34.048 position:24% line:89% align:start
I can say the same.

00:18:34.082 --> 00:18:34.849 position:21% line:89% align:start
The truth is that...

00:18:35.883 --> 00:18:37.351 position:21% line:83% align:start
Thankfully, the ball
came my way.

00:18:37.384 --> 00:18:39.087 position:35% line:83% align:start
It was luck
more than anything.

00:18:39.921 --> 00:18:41.388 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:18:43.524 --> 00:18:44.525 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:18:48.029 --> 00:18:49.063 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:18:49.097 --> 00:18:51.131 position:30% line:83% align:start
Until I become
a professional player...

00:18:51.164 --> 00:18:53.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
I won't be stepping
on this field...

00:18:53.433 --> 00:18:54.434 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:18:55.837 --> 00:18:56.904 position:38% line:83% align:start
Genzo...
I, um...

00:18:57.839 --> 00:18:59.206 position:33% line:89% align:start
I decided...

00:18:59.239 --> 00:19:00.875 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uh...
-Uh...

00:19:02.977 --> 00:19:03.310 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:19:04.378 --> 00:19:06.848 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have decided to stay
in Japan with everyone.

00:19:06.881 --> 00:19:09.282 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laugh]
-Yeah! I love you!

00:19:09.316 --> 00:19:11.184 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laugh]
-Yeah!

00:19:11.218 --> 00:19:12.352 position:27% line:83% align:start
We'll be able to
keep playing

00:19:12.386 --> 00:19:14.321 position:19% line:89% align:start
by our captain's side.

00:19:14.354 --> 00:19:16.490 position:21% line:83% align:start
I won't ever give up
on my dream.

00:19:16.524 --> 00:19:18.358 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm going to play for
Nankatsu's middle school,

00:19:18.392 --> 00:19:20.995 position:19% line:83% align:start
and one day, I'll go to
Brazil on my own merit.

00:19:21.029 --> 00:19:22.229 position:24% line:89% align:start
That sounds great.

00:19:22.262 --> 00:19:23.698 position:19% line:83% align:start
So then, the next time
we play together

00:19:23.731 --> 00:19:26.034 position:24% line:83% align:start
will be when we're
representing our country.

00:19:26.067 --> 00:19:27.267 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:19:34.676 --> 00:19:36.644 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>We'll see each other again.</i>

00:19:36.678 --> 00:19:37.912 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Until then, Tsubasa.</i>

00:19:43.985 --> 00:19:45.620 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Three years later.</i>

00:19:47.421 --> 00:19:50.124 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Katagiri] <i>Genzo Wakabayashi</i>
 <i>managed to stop the penalty</i>

00:19:50.158 --> 00:19:51.959 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>in yesterday's game.</i>

00:19:51.993 --> 00:19:53.393 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's a step away</i>
 <i>from becoming</i>

00:19:53.427 --> 00:19:55.163 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>the starter goalie</i>
 <i>for the second team</i>

00:19:55.195 --> 00:19:56.898 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>in his German school.</i>

00:19:56.931 --> 00:19:57.932 position:41% line:89% align:start
[reac]

00:19:57.965 --> 00:19:59.232 position:35% line:89% align:start
Excellent.

00:20:03.971 --> 00:20:05.173 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Teppei]
Hey, Ishizaki!

00:20:05.205 --> 00:20:06.273 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[narr] <i>Nankatsu</i>
-[Ryo] Hello!

