- <i>Middle School.</i>
-[Teppei] Did you get to

00:20:07.340 --> 00:20:08.876 position:13% line:89% align:start
rest up during the summer?

00:20:08.910 --> 00:20:09.476 position:35% line:89% align:start
Not at all.

00:20:10.444 --> 00:20:12.212 position:16% line:83% align:start
