enough to recover fully.

00:20:20.822 --> 00:20:22.489 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yeah, three days isn't much.

00:20:22.523 --> 00:20:24.458 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, now that Tsubasa
is playing with us,

00:20:24.491 --> 00:20:25.860 position:16% line:83% align:start
it's rare to lose a game
at all,

00:20:25.893 --> 00:20:28.328 position:16% line:83% align:start
but even then, they never
give us an easy game.

00:20:28.361 --> 00:20:29.864 position:38% line:83% align:start
Exactly.
Never.

00:20:29.897 --> 00:20:30.832 position:35% line:89% align:start
Stop lying.

00:20:30.865 --> 00:20:32.600 position:21% line:83% align:start
I heard that Tsubasa
got called to be in

00:20:32.633 --> 00:20:35.002 position:19% line:83% align:start
a special training camp
with the players of...

00:20:35.036 --> 00:20:36.403 position:21% line:89% align:start
Good morning, Sanae.

00:20:36.938 --> 00:20:37.672 position:33% line:89% align:start
Good morning.

00:20:38.740 --> 00:20:40.742 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Katagiri] <i>The center</i>
 <i>forwards of Nankatsu,</i>

00:20:40.775 --> 00:20:43.544 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Izawa, Kisugi, Taki</i>
 <i>and Takasugi</i>

00:20:43.578 --> 00:20:45.613 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>got into the same school</i>
 <i>as Tsubasa</i>

00:20:45.646 --> 00:20:47.715 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>with the mindset of</i>
 <i>improving their skills</i>

00:20:47.749 --> 00:20:49.550 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and becoming better</i>
 <i>as a team.</i>

00:20:49.584 --> 00:20:51.786 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even we are talking about</i>
 <i>a public school,</i>

00:20:51.819 --> 00:20:53.921 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>they now have</i>
 <i>the best soccer team</i>

00:20:53.955 --> 00:20:54.856 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>in the region.</i>

00:20:55.790 --> 00:20:56.657 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>On the other hand,</i>

00:20:56.691 --> 00:21:00.027 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Urabe, Kishida, Nishio,</i>
 <i>and Nakayama</i>

00:21:00.061 --> 00:21:02.230 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>from the old</i>
 <i>Nankatsu team...</i>

00:21:02.262 --> 00:21:04.565 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>got into Otomo</i>
 <i>Middle School.</i>

00:21:04.599 --> 00:21:06.399 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Now they're Nankatsu</i>
 <i>Middle School's rivals,</i>

00:21:06.433 --> 00:21:08.368 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and they're lead by</i>
 <i>someone very different</i>

00:21:08.401 --> 00:21:09.369 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>from Tsubasa.</i>

